sif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/stable/esp32/api-guides/unit-tests.html#applica=
tion-examples" title=3D"Permalink to this heading">=EF=83=81</a></h2>
<p><a class=3D"reference external" href=3D"https://github.com/espressif/esp=
-idf/tree/v6.0.2/examples/system/unit_test">system/unit_test</a> demonstrat=
es how to use the Unity library to add unit tests to custom components in a=
n ESP32 development environment, showcasing features such as assertions, te=
st registration, and the use of UNITY_BEGIN() and UNITY_END() macros.</p>
